Dr
Farid Kamal Ramzi Stino bụ ọkà mmụta sayensị, ọkà mmụta na onye ọchụnta ego nke Ijipt mụrụ na Cairo, Egypt na Septemba 1, 1943
Ọ bụ nwa Dr
Kamal Ramzi Stino, onye osote onye isi ala Ijipt nwụrụ anwụ n'okpuru ọchịchị Nasser
na Lady Farida Shawky Shenouda, ada Shawkey BEK Shenouda nke Ijipt
O nwetara nzere bachelọ nke sayensị na Mahadum Cairo dị n'Ijipt n'afọ 1964
Ọ gakwara mba Amerịka wee nweta nzere Master of Science na 1968 wee nweta Ph.D
nzere na 1971, site na Mahadum Georgia, na Athens, Georgia, USA
Ọ bụ n'ebe ahụ ka ọ zutere ma lụọ nwunye ya nke dị afọ 33, Dr
Zandra Hargrove Stino
O nwere ụmụ ise dị ndụ: Ramzi, Farida, Karim, Magdi na Farrah
Ọ bụ nna nna hụrụ n'anya nke Jadon Stino Gibson, Martino Ramzi Stino, Natalia Stino Gibson, Mario Ramzi Stino, na Austen Karim Stino
Dr
Stino bụ onye isi na onye isi oche nke Ismailia-Misr Poultry Company, otu n'ime ụlọ ọrụ anụ ọkụkọ kachasị na Middle East
Ọ bụkwa onye nwe na onye guzobere Stino Farms, nke dabere na Cairo.[] Ọ tọrọ ntọala Stino Agriconsults, ụlọ ọrụ na-ahụ maka ọrụ ugbo nke nwere ihe karịrị ndị ọkachamara 25, gụnyere Dr
Nageeb Goher, onye bụbu onyeisi oche nke Mahadum Cairo na Dr
Gamal Kamar bụbu Prọfesọ nke anụ ọkụkọ anụ ọkụkọ na Dr
Hamdy Mourad, onye na-ahụ maka anụ ahụ anụ ọhịa
Dọkịnta Stino kuziri ọzụzụ anụ ọkụkọ na mkpụrụ ndụ ihe nketa na Mahadum Cairo
Ọ kụzikwara Biostatistics na Kọmputa Methodology, dị ka onye nleta nleta, na Florida Agriculture and Mechanical University (FAMU) na Tallahassee Florida, USA afọ iri na abụọ malite 1988
Ọ laghachiri na Cairo University na 2000 na-isi na Department of Animal Production, Faculty of Agriculture, Cairo University
Iri na abụọ Ph.D
ụmụ akwụkwọ na iri abụọ na isii M.S
ụmụ akwụkwọ gụsịrị akwụkwọ n'okpuru nlekọta ya
O nwere ihe karịrị akụkọ 65 ebipụtara na akwụkwọ nyocha ndị ọgbọ
Ọchịchọ ya maka mkpụrụ ndụ ihe nketa na anụ ọkụkọ dugara ya ka ọ bụrụ injinia wee mepụta ụwa naanị anụ quail na-acha ọcha, nke dịkarịa ala okpukpu abụọ nke quail ọhịa
A na-achọsi ike Stino quail na mpaghara niile ma na-ere ya n'ụlọ nri kpakpando ise, ụlọ oriri na ọṅụṅụ na ahịa
Ọ na-anọ afọ ezumike nka ya ka na-akụzi Biostatistcs na Mahadum Cairo.
